Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:03:00.51,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(1098,599)}暴風雨之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不允許搜索里亞贊少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索下級士官有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 還是要優先尋找多爾傑夫閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都還不知道墜落到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是被擊落的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔基姆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體的修理和補給一結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就馬上和搜索隊匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對死人獻媚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我不能允許對青葉君進行搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面可是暴風雨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要盡快找到青葉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上天氣惡劣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是脫離了戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人可能也還在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,valiancer和Cygnus也並非毫無損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最優先考慮成員們的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的判斷有錯嗎 李君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…聯結機要兩台齊備才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是權衡一切之後的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦將繼續保持警戒態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴風雨過後 開始移動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,valiancer隊為了以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以隨時可以出擊的狀態待機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還像個孩子一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是不讓他幹 就越是想要幹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是強硬撬開了逐漸沉沒的座艙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你拉出來帶到了這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要俘虜你 證明我的清白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣怎麼說都動不了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包好像也被沖走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要調查一下你的valiancer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是聯結機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像出故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也拿到了救生包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟 能使用無線電的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等天晴了再詳細調查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一點感謝之情都沒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想說終於見到你了 這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俘虜不要多說廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個放下啊 話說那個本來就是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被奪走了救生包 你是個不稱職的軍人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在是軍人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會讓這種人搭乘新型機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為被你帶來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校突然被valiancer襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你救了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 說「迪奧在等你」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我送到這裡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,70年後的這個世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然讓這種男人當新型機的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合看來相當缺人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:06:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:06:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 你為什麼會知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 你是我的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫弓原雛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被valiancer襲擊的時候 你救了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同學？救你？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淨說些莫名其妙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事我要先告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你說的雛跟我有多麼相像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是配屬於佐基利亞軍第101獨立偵查旅團的少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維克多·里亞贊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我10歲就讀於第11幼年士官學校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業後 經利佩茨克基地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配屬於第501機動中隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能和你有過接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑啊 那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了見到雛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就交由我軍調查部來調查你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過暴風圈了 現在可以飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不算回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能失去LUXON
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長有話托我轉告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三小時為限
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過了三小時就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是連迪奧也行蹤不明就麻煩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有句話叫適得其反啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有另外一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾維拉小姐托我轉告的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定 聯結機器可以幫上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒找到多爾傑夫閣下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在進行搜索 但是還沒有找到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被擊落在一望無際的大海中的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒那種事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 野牛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 不是說FORTUNA啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是墜落而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心說話 塔基姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野牛和我們不同 從小就認識雛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和雛雖然是同一個班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻基本沒怎麼說過話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她救我的時候差不多是第一次說話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 我連她是什麼樣的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想見到她之後 問她很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要救我之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎樣才能回到原本的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我以為終於見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻告訴我是另外一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 她去了哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然已經不能回到原本的時代了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把火滅了 什麼都看不到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吵 閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 是被風吹滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得包裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被堵住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說 幸好火滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有空氣循環
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚會缺氧的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在挖沙土
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想和敵人白白死在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起一個人幹 還是兩個人更快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把這個切斷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我什麼都不會做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想死在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是稍微有一點奇怪的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 我不會那麼做的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 要挖多少才能出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖來挖去 馬上就從上面掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 休息結束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看原籃球部的體力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙…沙土從上面掉到了下面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定頂點附近 沙土更薄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是親衛師團長的機體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟預想一樣的結果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野牛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後 我們部隊將採取獨自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師團長閣下的戰死已確認
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務應該已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒找到？差不多要到三小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說被海流沖走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就要重新計算搜索範圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是還活著 就趕快發出求救信號啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸困難了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作一點 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說缺氧了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會讓你死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣…死在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上帶你上岸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包被沖走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次真的一無所有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞穴也在海中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在這裡等暴風雨過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉…青…聽到…回話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 捕捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧聯絡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現青葉同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 聯結系統真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然可以通過數倍擴大聯結可能領域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特定同伴機的位置 遠距離啟動它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼原理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 當然是開玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這個模式消耗能量非常厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說三小時 卻沒能回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後 我會嚴重警告他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手下留情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也找到了 可喜可賀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告情況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊怎麼樣了 敵人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵…敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 快點報告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然電波狀態…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐基利亞的通信周波數是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要取得聯絡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要告訴佐基利亞 雛在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 捕捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美啊 就算過了70年 朝陽也不會改變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:19:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要讓我聯繫佐基利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那樣的話 雛就會成為我們的俘虜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個不稱職的軍人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧好像來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊也有人來接吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就趕快藏起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雛的髮夾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是飛到這邊的時候 一起帶著的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不是那個雛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我想讓你拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:20:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你可以走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫渡瀨青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 喲 辛苦你們來接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 切斷通信是想幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊 電波狀態突然變糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種謊話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦 青葉君平安歸來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會再問你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這話迪奧可以說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快回收
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等啊 我還沒坐上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡瀨…青葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:40.16,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(631,474)}下回「聯結系統」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 BUDDY COMPLEX 聯結系統
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:23.23,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で呼ぶ　惹かれあう彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:23.23,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心的呼應 響應的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:31.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛みの理由(わけ)も忘れて　今だけどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:31.88,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛的理由 請暫且忘記 我在此深深祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:41.08,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミを知っている　キミを探しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:41.08,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深知你 我在一直尋找著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.12,0:22:49.80,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引き止められない光の残像に　そっとくちづけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.12,0:22:49.80,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕吻向那已飄渺的光的殘像
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:58.81,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躊躇いが僅かな　希望への糸口なら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:58.81,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那稍稍的猶豫不決 成為了那連接希望的蛛絲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:07.52,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨った数だけ　優しい朝へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:07.52,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那微微的彷徨 拉近了與那溫柔黎明的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:16.56,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの空に還る未来で　救いたい　守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:16.56,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去拯救 想去保護 那早已歸還於天空的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.57,0:23:23.44,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その夢に届く未来で　待っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.57,0:23:23.44,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請留步 那已經早已傳達過夢想的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:32.86,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと出会える愛に　手を伸ばして欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:32.86,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能與我一起去抓住 那注定相遇的愛